&lt;img src=&quot;res/sk_blafp/common/rightarrow.gif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt; Setup :&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;  Hierarchical aggregation rules are set up directly in the logical layer of an Oracle BIEE RPD, by leveraging distinct physical aliases of the fact table.</sawd:HTML>
